======================================================================
β₃ AND β₅ COEXISTENCE CHECK
======================================================================
From prior data: H=3255 has β₃=1, H=3075 has β₅=2. Are these β₃ AND β₅ at once?
β₃ would need S-phase (3-cycle structure), β₅ is higher-dimensional.
From beta5_n9_check: H=3075 has β=[1,0,0,0,4,2] — β₃=0, β₅=2. So NO coexistence.
H=3255 has β=[1,0,0,1,0,0] — β₃=1, β₅=0. Also NO coexistence.
This preserves mutual exclusivity of odd Betti numbers at n=9.

Total time: 3399.2s
